3.0.2.name: wordpress/font-awesome-more-icons
3.0.2.description:
Font Awesome More (Fontstrap) is a pictographic font set of over 400 icons. It includes all icons from the Font Awesome set, plus additional icons from the Fontstrap extension set. The icons are infitinely scalable and screen reader compatible.

A full list of all 400+ icons is available here:

Font Awesome icons
Font Awesome More (Fontstrap) icons
